onal insight into the group process, both for therapists and clinicians and for women wishing to better understand their addiction"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 29 0aWomen gamblers. 0aCompulsive gambling.  aHV 6713 K37 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035207719  aHV 6713 K37 2015wLCc1i0162035207719lON_SHELFmUAAUGp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu1/6/2015  aHV6713 .K37 2015wLCc1i1007433657d1/23/2015lON_SHELFmGR_MACEWANp$48.37rYsYtBOOKu1/20/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2012062603bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/264923769